00:08:38.909 --> 00:08:41.659
of the surface in the
corresponding location where

00:08:41.659 --> 00:08:43.049
the ray hits the axis.

00:08:43.049 --> 00:08:45.840
So you can imagine it will
become a very complicated kind

00:08:45.840 --> 00:08:47.020
of situation.

00:08:47.020 --> 00:08:51.180
So typically we
don't deal with this.

00:08:51.180 --> 00:08:56.456
