00:26:41.550 --> 00:26:47.910
it applies as we discussed
not only on a thick lens

00:26:47.910 --> 00:26:51.330
but in general in any
compound optical system that

00:26:51.330 --> 00:26:54.210
contains multiple
elements like this one.

00:26:54.210 --> 00:26:58.180
And in order to utilize it,
what you do is you throw out,

00:26:58.180 --> 00:27:01.350
so to speak, all of this
