00:59:13.420 --> 00:59:17.930
This is this displacement here,
with respect to the center

00:59:17.930 --> 00:59:19.300
of the coordinates.

00:59:19.300 --> 00:59:21.400
And then what do you
do, this is [INAUDIBLE]

00:59:21.400 --> 00:59:23.410
slide but I will
actually derive it

00:59:23.410 --> 00:59:27.070
for you here so you can see it
in this sort of animated form.

00:59:27.070 --> 00:59:28.690
And then what you
do is you actually

00:59:28.690 --> 00:59:37.555
solve, so you have an s
equals plus/minus R minus--

00:59:40.493 --> 00:59:41.160
what am I doing?

00:59:41.160 --> 00:59:45.090
AUDIENCE: So you've got
your axis-- your [INAUDIBLE]

