01:05:02.870 --> 01:05:06.150
Can you imagine how I could
construct a mirror forming

01:05:06.150 --> 01:05:08.360
a virtual image?

01:05:16.724 --> 01:05:19.340
AUDIENCE: If the mirror
diverges and you are looking

01:05:19.340 --> 01:05:21.010
